  "detailed_description": "ThumBeat: Button Basher Edition is a short-form, button-bashing rhythm game for busy people! Button Basher takes your preferred button bashing techniques to the max!<br><br>Key Features:<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1790640/extras/13be404384dba6e420b0599a20a4022f.avif?t=1653702631\" width=600 height=100 /></span><br>Choose from over 25 songs exclusive in rhythm games with multiple genres ranging from chiptune/8-bit to guitar!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1790640/extras/4b74be9980b9aad82266a1e7433f669c.avif?t=1653702631\" width=600 height=100 /></span><br>Play each song at four different difficulty levels. Can you take each song to the Xtreme?<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1790640/extras/e22023e46b98d2aa42d3725f4b4e0d3b.avif?t=1653702631\" width=600 height=100 /></span><br>Be on top of the world with your high scores on the global leaderboards!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1790640/extras/4fe4ca86c027f3a19555ed1c5d829860.avif?t=1653702631\" width=600 height=100 /></span><br>Play each song with touchscreen, mouse, keyboard or gamepad! Can you master the songs in all 4 controller modes?<br><br>- Super expert? Push the speed multiplier up and see if you can still withstand the gameplay!",
